summary: Completed comprehensive testing of OMNISupply.io enterprise e-commerce platform. Backend APIs are 100% functional. Frontend has minor ChatBot interaction issue due to overlay element but core functionality works well.

ui_bugs.issue: ChatBot button not clickable due to emergent badge overlay intercepting pointer events

design_issues.issue: Product search returned 0 results for 'bearing' query, may need better mock data distribution

passed_tests: Backend API - All 19 endpoints working (100% success rate)
Landing page loads with all sections (hero, stats, categories, brands, services, integrations)
Login flow with demo credentials works correctly
Catalog page loads and displays properly
Services tab and service cards display
Navigation between pages (orders, rewards, bulk upload)
action_item_for_main_agent: Minor fix needed: Remove or adjust emergent badge overlay that prevents ChatBot button clicks. Consider improving product search mock data distribution for better demo experience.
